Introduction to Probability


sample(0:9,1)

[1] 3
sample(0:9,7,replace=TRUE)

[1] 4 2 2 6 9 9 1
rbinom(1,100,0.20)

[1] 13
rbinom(1,1000,0.20)

[1] 184
rbinom(1,10000,0.20)

[1] 1968
rbinom(1,100000,0.20)

[1] 20011
rbinom(1,1000000,0.20)

[1] 200172














